file_content.text: You dare invade my private chambers?
Your lesson in torment begins now.
Do you like my corruptions? Haha!
I'm done toying with you.
Dying already? I overestimated you.
One of you has fallen. Hardly surprising.
In the end, all existence will fall to us....
There is no end to the suffering you'll endure!
Enjoy this momentary victory. It will be your last....
This is the best that could be sent against us?
You bore me.
Embrace the darkness!
Consume them! Consume them all!
Your flesh will fuel my pets!
Would you prefer a more dangerous threat?
Acquaint yourselves with new ways to die.
One of us has fallen. He will be the last!
My pets are legion! Behold!
Drink of my corruption!
One succumbs to my corruption.
